    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2022-05-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2023-08-15T17:40:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Lifting Immigrant Families Through Benefits Access Restoration Act of 2022 or the LIFT the BAR Act of </strong><b>2022</b></p> <p>This bill repeals certain limits on the eligibility of noncitizens who lawfully reside in the United States for federal means-tested programs, including Medicaid, the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP), programs funded through Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF) grants, Supplemental Security Income (SSI), and certain nutrition and housing programs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
